          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Though you pound a fool in a mortar with a pestle along with crushed grain, Yet his foolishness will not depart from him. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
